summary:
- 6+ years of experience as Full Stack Developer in Telecom Domain.
- Specialized in Billing application and SAAS application.
- Experienced in following/implementing Agile/DevOps.
- Experienced in Scoping HLD/DD preparation for new development as well as a change request.
- Experience with microservice architecture.
- Experience in readable and optimized code development with good knowledge of data structure, design
- pattern and Algorithms.
- Experience with TDD development
